OL,3,CSome motorists who pay monthly for
OL,4,Cinsurance 'charged annual rates close
OL,5,Cto 30%'
OL,7,FPremium finance is widely used across
OL,8,Fthe market with charges that can
OL,9,Fdiffer between insurers and by product.
OL,11,F"Our members remain committed to
OL,12,Fimproving outcomes, and this includes
OL,13,Fbeing open about the fact that
OL,14,Fproviding this service involves
OL,15,Fgenuine operational costs ` including
OL,16,Fkeeping cover in place for a period
OL,17,Feven when payments are delayed or
OL,18,Fmissed.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
