CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781576262
OL,3,CSome motorists who pay monthly for
OL,4,Cinsurance 'charged annual rates close
OL,5,Cto 30%'
OL,7,F"Our premium finance principles make
OL,8,Fclear that any charges must be fair,
OL,9,Ftransparent, and reflective of the
OL,10,Fcosts incurred by insurers. The FCA's
OL,11,F(Financial Conduct Authority's) own
OL,12,Fmarket study found that premium
OL,13,Ffinance can deliver fair value for
OL,14,Fconsumers and that the overall cost of
OL,15,Fpremium finance has fallen since 2022."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@gO]
